-5" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-5" class="mw-reference-text">Herodotus, Herodotus, trans. A.D. Godley, vol. 4, book 8, verse 98, pp. 96–97 (1924).</span></li><li about="#cite_note-6" id="cite_note-6"><a href="./Mail#cite_ref-6" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-6" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt21" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite web ","href":"./Template:Cite_web"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"http://www.firstissues.org/ficc/details/scinde_1.shtml"},"title":{"wt":"First Issues Collectors Club of stamps and philatelic material"},"accessdate":{"wt":"2007-07-28"},"deadurl":{"wt":"no"},"archiveurl":{"wt":"https://archive.is/20120904135544/http://www.firstissues.org/ficc/details/scinde_1.shtml"},"archivedate":{"wt":"2012-09-04"},"df":{"wt":""}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAf8"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.firstissues.org/ficc/details/scinde_1.shtml" id="mwAgA">"First Issues Collectors Club of stamps and philatelic material"</a>. <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://archive.is/20120904135544/http://www.firstissues.org/ficc/details/scinde_1.shtml" id="mwAgE">Archived</a> from the original on 2012-09-04<span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwAgI">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwAgM">2007-07-28</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=First+Issues+Collectors+Club+of+stamps+and+philatelic+material&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.firstissues.org%2Fficc%2Fdetails%2Fscinde_1.shtml&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMail" class="Z3988" about="#mwt21" id="mwAgQ"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt21" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"nam